<br>
Of course this was nerfed, and the nerf was overkill.  Then about a year ago it was slightly unnerfed, but still sucks.  The way the rains work now is you get either 3 waves (on 1 target), or you get 4 things hit (counting them more than once if hit by more than 1 wave), including hitting yourself if you are in the AE range.<br>
<br>
P.S. because the AE rains were so badly broken for so long, they also overcompensated when giving rains more damage with the Kunark spells.  AE rains between levels 51 and 60 all have better mana/damage ratios than single target DD spells, even if only 1 target gets hit by the AE. <p><H1>Shamoo</H1><br>
